# Read in the Health Retirement 2020's data 

## Section A: Coverscreen(Respondent)
HRS2020_coverscreen=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20a_r.dta')

## Section B: Demographic information
HRS2020_demographic = pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20b_r.dta')

## Section COV: Covid19
HRS2020_covid=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20cov_r.dta')

## Section E:Family Structure(Children),Family Structure(Children) and Transfers(To Child), Family Structure(Children) and Transfers(From Child)
HRS2020_family=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20e_h.dta')
HRS2020_transfertochildren=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20e_tc.dta')
HRS2020_transferfromchildren=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20e_fc.dta')

## Section J,J2,J3
##J:Employment(Respondent)
HRS2020_employment=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20j_r.dta')
##J2:Pension(Pension)
HRS2020_pension=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20j2_p.dta')
##J3:Retirement(Respondent)
HRS2020_retirement=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20j3_r.dta')

## Section N: Health Services and Insurance (Respondent)
HRS2020_insurance=pd.read_stata('Data/HRS_2020/h20sta/h20n_r.dta')
